---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const locale = 'es';
---

<Layout 
  title="Gaia Commons | El Alma"
  description="El alma de una civilización que renace. Gobernanza, principios y capital estratégico — todo lo que sostiene y dirige al ecosistema."
  keywords={["Gaia Commons", "gobernanza distribuida", "capital regenerativo", "principios", "orquestación de impacto", "DAO"]}
  schemaType={["WebPage", "Organization"]}
>
  
  <!-- Top Navigation Shell -->
  <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-[#fefee5]/80 backdrop-blur-xl shadow-[0_40px_60px_-5px_rgba(54,59,16,0.06)]">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center max-w-[1618px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] h-24">
      <a href="/es/" class="text-3xl font-black text-primary px-6 font-headline tracking-tight">
        Gaia
      </a>
      <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-12 font-headline tracking-tight font-bold uppercase text-sm">
        <a class="text-on-surface/70 hover:text-on-surface transition-colors" href="/es/">Inicio</a>
        <a class="text-on-surface/70 hover:text-on-surface transition-colors" href="/es/hub">Hub</a>
        <a class="text-on-surface/70 hover:text-on-surface transition-colors" href="/es/market">Market</a>
        <a class="text-primary border-b-2 border-primary pb-1" href="/es/commons">Commons</a>
        <div class="relative group">
          <a class="text-on-surface/70 hover:text-on-surface transition-colors flex items-center gap-1" href="/es/commons">
            Impact
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">expand_more</span>
          </a>
          <div class="absolute top-full left-0 pt-2 opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all duration-200">
            <div class="bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-xl shadow-xl border border-outline/10 py-2 min-w-[180px]">
              <a class="block px-4 py-2 text-on-surface/70 hover:text-primary hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors text-xs" href="/es/commons/impact-fund/">Impact Fund</a>
              <a class="block px-4 py-2 text-on-surface/70 hover:text-primary hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors text-xs" href="/es/commons/impact-hub/">Impact Hub</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a href="#comunidad" class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-headline font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider hover:opacity-90 transition-all scale-95 active:scale-90">
          Únete
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="pt-24">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[800px] flex items-center overflow-hidden px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] py-24">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-surface/20 to-surface z-10"></div>
        <div class="w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506905925346-21bda4d32df4?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-20 max-w-[1000px] w-full">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 mb-8 rounded-full bg-secondary-container/40 text-on-secondary-container font-label text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase backdrop-blur-sm">
          El Alma del Ecosistema
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-on-surface leading-[1.1] mb-8 tracking-tighter">
          El alma de una civilización que <span class="text-primary italic">renace</span>.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-on-surface/70 max-w-2xl font-light leading-relaxed mb-12">
          Gobernanza, principios y capital estratégico — todo lo que sostiene y dirige al ecosistema Gaia hacia un futuro regenerativo.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6">
          <a href="#funciones" class="px-10 py-5 solar-gradient text-white rounded-xl font-headline font-bold text-lg shadow-xl hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-transform">
            Explorar los Principios
          </a>
          <a href="#comunidad" class="px-10 py-5 bg-surface-container-highest text-on-surface rounded-xl font-headline font-bold text-lg hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors">
            Hablar con el Equipo
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stewardship & System -->
    <section class="py-24 lg:py-32 px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] bg-surface-container-low">
      <div class="max-w-[1618px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="aspect-[1.618/1] bg-surface-container-high rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative group">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/10 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500"></div>
            <img alt="Permaculture garden" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1466692476868-aef1dfb1e735?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"/>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8 leading-tight">Commons-based Coordination System.</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-on-surface/70 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
            Gaia Commons no es una estructura de control, sino un organismo de <span class="text-secondary font-bold">Stewardship</span>. Diseñamos sistemas de coordinación donde el bien común y la soberanía individual coexisten en armonía a través de una arquitectura policéntrica.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-6">
            <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">hub</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl">Stewardship > Ownership</h4>
                <p class="text-on-surface/70">Priorizamos el cuidado y la custodia de los activos sobre la propiedad extractiva.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">account_balance</span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl">Polycentric Governance</h4>
                <p class="text-on-surface/70">Múltiples centros de decisión coordinados por protocolos de confianza radical.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Four Functions Bento Grid -->
    <section id="funciones" class="py-24 lg:py-32 px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem]">
      <div class="max-w-[1618px] mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 lg:mb-24">
          <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-6">Funciones Vitales</h2>
          <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-primary mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
          <!-- Function 1: Principios -->
          <div class="md:col-span-7 bg-surface-container rounded-xl p-10 lg:p-12 relative overflow-hidden group">
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-primary mb-6" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">shield_with_heart</span>
              <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black mb-4 uppercase tracking-tighter">Principios (Guardianship)</h3>
              <p class="text-on-surface/70 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md">La brújula ética que asegura que cada acción esté alineada con la regeneración de la biosfera y el florecimiento humano.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute -right-20 -bottom-20 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[15rem] text-primary">shield_with_heart</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Function 2: Gobernanza -->
          <div class="md:col-span-5 bg-surface-container-high rounded-xl p-10 lg:p-12 flex flex-col justify-end">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-tertiary mb-6">account_tree</span>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black mb-4 uppercase tracking-tighter">Gobernanza (DAOs/Councils)</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">Arquitecturas descentralizadas para la toma de decisiones colectiva, fluida y transparente.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Function 3: Capital -->
          <div class="md:col-span-5 bg-surface-variant/30 rounded-xl p-10 lg:p-12">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-secondary mb-6">currency_exchange</span>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black mb-4 uppercase tracking-tighter">Capital (Fund deployment)</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">Asignación inteligente de recursos financieros para maximizar el retorno sistémico.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Function 4: Orquestación -->
          <div class="md:col-span-7 bg-surface-container-highest rounded-xl p-10 lg:p-12 flex items-center gap-6 lg:gap-8">
            <div class="hidden lg:flex w-28 h-28 rounded-full border-4 border-primary/20 items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary">auto_awesome</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black mb-4 uppercase tracking-tighter">Orquestación de Impacto</h3>
              <p class="text-on-surface/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">Soluciones estratégicas que conectan problemas reales con capital y talento especializado.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Capital Flow -->
    <section class="py-24 lg:py-32 px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] bg-surface-container">
      <div class="max-w-[1618px] mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-black mb-16 uppercase tracking-widest text-primary">Flujo del Capital</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 md:gap-4">
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 lg:w-24 lg:h-24 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg mb-6">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-on-surface">verified</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-headline font-bold">Principles</h4>
            <div class="h-20 w-px bg-primary/20 my-3 hidden md:block"></div>
          </div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined md:rotate-0 rotate-90 text-primary opacity-30 text-4xl">arrow_forward</span>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 lg:w-24 lg:h-24 rounded-full bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg mb-6">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-on-primary-container">monetization_on</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-headline font-bold">Strategic Capital</h4>
            <div class="h-20 w-px bg-primary/20 my-3 hidden md:block"></div>
          </div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined md:rotate-0 rotate-90 text-primary opacity-30 text-4xl">arrow_forward</span>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 lg:w-24 lg:h-24 rounded-full bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg mb-6">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-on-secondary-container">account_balance_wallet</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-headline font-bold">Specialized Funds</h4>
            <div class="h-20 w-px bg-primary/20 my-3 hidden md:block"></div>
          </div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined md:rotate-0 rotate-90 text-primary opacity-30 text-4xl">arrow_forward</span>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 lg:w-32 lg:h-32 rounded-3xl bg-primary flex items-center justify-center shadow-2xl mb-6">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-white">nature_people</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-headline font-bold">Real Projects</h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Difference / Value Prop -->
    <section class="py-24 lg:py-32 px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] overflow-hidden">
      <div class="max-w-[1618px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-12">Lo que nos hace <span class="text-tertiary">diferentes</span>.</h2>
          <div class="space-y-10 lg:space-y-12">
            <div class="flex gap-6 lg:gap-8">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-tertiary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary text-3xl">all_inclusive</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl lg:text-2xl mb-2">Multi-capital Approach</h4>
                <p class="text-on-surface/70">No solo medimos el éxito en dinero. Evaluamos capital natural, social, cultural e intelectual como activos reales.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-6 lg:gap-8">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl">vibration</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl lg:text-2xl mb-2">Evolutionary Nature</h4>
                <p class="text-on-surface/70">Nuestros protocolos de gobernanza no son estáticos; están diseñados para aprender y adaptarse al ecosistema en tiempo real.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-surface-container-high p-8 lg:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-inner relative z-10">
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold mb-8">Para inversores y aliados</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface/70 mb-8 text-lg">Invertir en Gaia Commons es participar en la construcción de la infraestructura real del mañana. Ofrecemos un retorno múltiple: financiero, ecológico y social.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-6 bg-white/50 rounded-2xl">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl">foundation</span>
              <span class="font-bold">Infraestructura Real & Regenerativa</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-64 h-64 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-0"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-12 -left-12 w-64 h-64 bg-tertiary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-0"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section id="comunidad" class="py-24 lg:py-32 px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem]">
      <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto bg-inverse-surface text-inverse-on-surface rounded-[3rem] p-12 lg:p-24 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518495973542-4542c06a5843?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-10 leading-tight">¿Listo para ser parte de la <br/>nueva civilización?</h2>
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-4 lg:gap-6">
            <a href="https://t.me/+1x_EVaVp-lEwN2I8" target="_blank" class="px-10 lg:px-12 py-5 lg:py-6 solar-gradient text-white font-headline font-black text-lg rounded-full shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
              Explorar los Principios
            </a>
            <a href="https://t.me/+1x_EVaVp-lEwN2I8" target="_blank" class="px-10 lg:px-12 py-5 lg:py-6 border-2 border-inverse-on-surface/30 text-inverse-on-surface font-headline font-black text-lg rounded-full hover:bg-inverse-on-surface/10 transition-colors">
              Hablar con el Equipo
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="w-full py-[5.5rem] bg-surface-container">
    <div class="max-w-[1618px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1.618fr_1fr] gap-12 px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem]">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="font-headline font-bold text-primary text-2xl tracking-tight">
          Gaia Ecosystem
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface/60 max-w-sm">
          Infraestructura para una civilización regenerativa. Un ecosistema descentralizado de coordinación planetaria.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-on-surface/40">
          © 2026 Gaia Ecosystem.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 font-body text-sm">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Explorar</span>
          <a class="text-on-surface/60 hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/es/hub">Gaia Hub</a>
          <a class="text-on-surface/60 hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/es/market">Gaia Market</a>
          <a class="text-on-surface/60 hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/es/commons">Gaia Commons</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Comunidad</span>
          <a class="text-on-surface/60 hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="https://t.me/+1x_EVaVp-lEwN2I8" target="_blank">Telegram</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  .material-symbols-outlined {
    font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
  }
  .solar-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #776300 0%, #ffd709 100%);
  }
</style>
